 Also, Figs. ~\ref{fig7} and ~\ref{fig8} indicate a similar mass ordering for $p+p$ systems which indicates that the system formed in most peripheral  A+A  collisions and $p+p$ collisions are of similar nature. Further, it hints the similarity in the evolution of both the systems. 

